name: Antonis Karatzias
note:
Description:We are going to discuss options for partnership in managing human resources for Dias Media Group  in Ukraine.

Website: rh-s.com
Company website:  http://www.diasmedia.com/index.php/home

Comments: Antonis Karatzias (https://www.linkedin.com/in/karatzias) is interested in our services 

Manager: Процив София

Result:
Company Name: Dias Media Group

Company Website: http://www.diasmedia.com/index.php/home

Contact Person: Antonis Karatzias

Product:  Dias Media Group is the largest media group in Cyprus, entertaining and informing on a daily basis its hundreds of thousands of viewers, readers, listeners and internet users via electronic and printed media.
At the same time, the Group has established commercial partnership agreements with the licensed companies Sigma TV Radio Public Ltd, the radio station Super FM and the online portal sigmalive.com.
Dias Media Group uses the latest technology for the production and supply of its services and products. Following high standards of creation and setting new standards of quality, the Group manages not only to effectively assess consumer preferences, but also meet consumer needs with absolute success.


Specialties:  Newspapers, Magazines, Online Portals, and Communications

Country-Location: Cyprus

Target Audience: Worldwide

Immediate Requirement: Antonis was interested in our services. He asked about our candidates, for now he is looking for lots of people in the Digital sphere. Some of them will be needed in July, some in the future. 

Next Step: We will send all information about our company.   By the end of next week Antonis will share with us a list of specialties he is looking for. 

Next Contact Date: keep in touch by email
